      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;There are so many different options now to raise your various stats that you can easily find a way to overcome any weakness you may have.  You can even add in AA's at level 51+ that raise your stats innately.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;I recomend putting most of your stats into stamina.  It never hurts to have as many hitpoints as you can.  It's not a big deal, but caster gear tends to steer more towards wis/int than stamina, so get what you can when you can.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Oh, and welcome back.&lt;/div&gt;</description>
